  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it's translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, turmeric, cinnamon, and black pepper powders and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until they're browned.",
    "Add the red lentils and water to the pan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in some salt to taste.",
